(184, 46, 'portfolio_items_1_portfolio_item', '<p class="p1" style="text-align: center;"><span class="s1"><a href="#">Bo Burlingham: </a><i><a href="#">Finish Big</a>\r\n</i></span>Website and Print Materials</p>\r\n<p class="p1" style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-24" src="http://localhost:8888/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/finishbig-mobile-preview-01.jpg" alt="finishbig-mobile-preview-01" /></p>\r\n<p class="p1" style="text-align: center;">Brief 2–3 line blurb about our work with\r\nBo Burlingham for his book <i>Finish Big.</i>\r\nBlue whales, grey whales, and orcas read Herman Melville to their children at night\r\nto discourage bad behavior.</p>'),
