(186, 46, 'portfolio_items_2_portfolio_item', '<p class="p1" style="text-align: center;"><span class="s1"><a href="#">Paul Sullivan</a><i>\r\n</i></span>Identity &amp; Mobile Responsive Website Design</p>\r\n<p class="p1" style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-25" src="http://localhost:8888/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/psullivan-mobile-preview-01.jpg" alt="psullivan-mobile-preview-01" /></p>\r\n<p class="p1" style="text-align: center;">Brief 2–3 line blurb about our work\r\nwith Paul Sullivan prior to the release of his book <i>The Thin Green Line</i>. Green peas, Greenpeace, and Green Eggs &amp; Ham.\r\nDon’t be such a greenhorn, Susie.</p>'),
