(298, 76, 'identity_design_story_0_identity_design_step', '<h4 class="p1">Early Sketching and Ideation</h4>\r\n<p class="p1">We paved the way for this project by working closely with the quartet’s members to find the words and images that best represented their powerful presence and playing style. With the quartet’s recordings playing through our speakers, we then began to jot our ideas down on paper, producing over fifty rough thumbnails for our team to consider.</p>'),
