(341, 78, 'identity_design_story_1_identity_design_step', '<h4 class="p1">Exploring Calligraphic Letterforms</h4>\r\n<p class="p1">The options that stood out the most were those composed of calligraphic letterforms. We pondered the parallels and differences between Eastern and Western calligraphy as we continued to hone in on the perfect glyph, employing our entire stash of pens and brushes along the way to find just the right stroke quality.</p>'),
