(467, 80, 'website_design_story_0_website_design_step', '<h4 class="p1">Photography Selection &amp; Integration</h4>\r\n<p class="p1">The Shanghai Quartet had plenty of publicity photos on hand when we met them, but none of these seemed to communicate the powerful energy of their performances. We worked closely with their photographer to develop a portfolio of live performance photos, which were used throughout the website for maximum impact.</p>'),
