(547, 83, 'website_design_story_1_website_design_step', '<h4 class="p1">Custom Performance Calendar</h4>\r\n<p class="p1">With their busy schedules, we knew that none of the quartet’s members would have the time to manually enter information on upcoming performances—so we made sure that their public calendar could be easily updated through Google Calendar, without sacrificing aesthetics or ease of use for those getting their information through the quartet’s website.</p>'),
(548, 83, '_website_design_story_1_website_design_step', 'field_54f5eef6bbe82'),
(549, 83, 'website_design_story_1_web_step_gallery_0_web_gallery_photo', '81'),
(550, 83, '_website_design_story_1_web_step_gallery_0_web_gallery_photo', 'field_54f63106ed2a7'),
(551, 83, 'website_design_story_1_web_step_gallery', '1'),
(552, 83, '_website_design_story_1_web_step_gallery', 'field_54f630eeed2a6'),
(553, 83, 'website_design_story_2_website_design_step', '<h4 class="p1">Mandarin Chinese Version of Website</h4>\r\n<p class="p1">Although we had previously designed websites using multiple European languages, this was our first step into the world of Asian typography. We performed our share of research to make sure we weren’t committing any major typographic faux pas in our use of Chinese characters, and carefully selected fonts that had a similar character and texture to those used on the English version of the site.</p>'),
(554, 83, '_website_design_story_2_website_design_step', 'field_54f5eef6bbe82'),
(555, 83, 'website_design_story_2_web_step_gallery_0_web_gallery_photo', '68'),
(556, 83, '_website_design_story_2_web_step_gallery_0_web_gallery_photo', 'field_54f63106ed2a7'),
