(562, 83, '_testimonial_image', 'field_54f5ef4cbbe83'),
(563, 83, 'testimonial', '<blockquote>\r\n<p class="p1"><i>The whole thing came\r\noff smoking!<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>Round Hex figured\r\nout a way to truly capture the\r\nessence of our quartet.</i></p>\r\n</blockquote>'),
(564, 83, '_testimonial', 'field_54f5ef89bbe84'),
(565, 47, 'website_design_story_1_website_design_step', '<h4 class="p1">Custom Performance Calendar</h4>\r\n<p class="p1">With their busy schedules, we knew that none of the quartet’s members would have the time to manually enter information on upcoming performances—so we made sure that their public calendar could be easily updated through Google Calendar, without sacrificing aesthetics or ease of use for those getting their information through the quartet’s website.</p>'),
