(633, 85, 'website_design_story_2_website_design_step', '<h4 class="p1">Mandarin Chinese Version of Website</h4>\r\n<p class="p1">Although we had previously designed websites using multiple European languages, this was our first step into the world of Asian typography. We performed our share of research to make sure we weren’t committing any major typographic faux pas in our use of Chinese characters, and carefully selected fonts that had a similar character and texture to those used on the English version of the site.</p>'),
(634, 85, '_website_design_story_2_website_design_step', 'field_54f5eef6bbe82'),
(635, 85, 'website_design_story_2_web_step_gallery_0_web_gallery_photo', '68'),
(636, 85, '_website_design_story_2_web_step_gallery_0_web_gallery_photo', 'field_54f63106ed2a7'),
(637, 85, 'website_design_story_2_web_step_gallery', '1'),
(638, 85, '_website_design_story_2_web_step_gallery', 'field_54f630eeed2a6'),
(639, 85, 'website_design_story', '3'),
(640, 85, '_website_design_story', 'field_54f5eee4bbe81'),
(641, 85, 'testimonial_image', '82'),
(642, 85, '_testimonial_image', 'field_54f5ef4cbbe83'),
(643, 85, 'testimonial', '<blockquote>\r\n<p class="p1"><i>The whole thing came\r\noff smoking!<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>Round Hex figured\r\nout a way to truly capture the\r\nessence of our quartet.</i></p>\r\n</blockquote>'),
(644, 85, '_testimonial', 'field_54f5ef89bbe84'),
(645, 85, 'testimonial_source', 'Nicholas Tzavaras,<br/>Cellist for the Shanghai Quartet'),
(646, 85, '_testimonial_source', 'field_54f69374477ea'),
(647, 47, 'testimonial_source', 'Nicholas Tzavaras,<br/>Cellist for the Shanghai Quartet'),
(648, 47, '_testimonial_source', 'field_54f69374477ea'),
(649, 86, 'hero_image', '48'),
(650, 86, '_hero_image', 'field_54f4f43264daa'),
(651, 86, 'work', 'Identity & Website Design'),
(652, 86, '_work', 'field_54f633eca4b47'),
(653, 86, 'identity_design_story_0_identity_design_step', '<h4 class="p1">Early Sketching and Ideation</h4>\r\n<p class="p1">We paved the way for this project by working closely with the quartet’s members to find the words and images that best represented their powerful presence and playing style. With the quartet’s recordings playing through our speakers, we then began to jot our ideas down on paper, producing over fifty rough thumbnails for our team to consider.</p>'),
(654, 86, '_identity_design_story_0_identity_design_step', 'field_54f5ee84bbe80'),
(655, 86, 'identity_design_story_0_step_gallery_0_gallery_photo', '75'),
(656, 86, '_identity_design_story_0_step_gallery_0_gallery_photo', 'field_54f630beed2a5'),
(657, 86, 'identity_design_story_0_step_gallery_1_gallery_photo', '73'),
(658, 86, '_identity_design_story_0_step_gallery_1_gallery_photo', 'field_54f630beed2a5'),
(659, 86, 'identity_design_story_0_step_gallery_2_gallery_photo', '74'),
(660, 86, '_identity_design_story_0_step_gallery_2_gallery_photo', 'field_54f630beed2a5'),
(661, 86, 'identity_design_story_0_step_gallery', '3'),
(662, 86, '_identity_design_story_0_step_gallery', 'field_54f630a5ed2a4'),
(663, 86, 'identity_design_story_1_identity_design_step', '<h4 class="p1">Exploring Calligraphic Letterforms</h4>\r\n<p class="p1">The options that stood out the most were those composed of calligraphic letterforms. We pondered the parallels and differences between Eastern and Western calligraphy as we continued to hone in on the perfect glyph, employing our entire stash of pens and brushes along the way to find just the right stroke quality.</p>'),
(664, 86, '_identity_design_story_1_identity_design_step', 'field_54f5ee84bbe80'),
(665, 86, 'identity_design_story_1_step_gallery_0_gallery_photo', '74'),
(666, 86, '_identity_design_story_1_step_gallery_0_gallery_photo', 'field_54f630beed2a5'),
(667, 86, 'identity_design_story_1_step_gallery', '1'),
(668, 86, '_identity_design_story_1_step_gallery', 'field_54f630a5ed2a4'),
(669, 86, 'identity_design_story_2_identity_design_step', '<h4 class="p1">Examining Cultural Roots</h4>\r\n<p class="p1">After presenting our top three choices to the client, this simple “SQ” monogram emerged as the clear favorite. Having selected a mark that reflected Western calligraphic traditions more than Eastern, we decided to explore our options for striking more of a balance between the two. The square seals traditionally used by Chinese painters came to mind almost immediately. Careful explorations of texture and composition followed, producing a wide array of variations which we again narrowed down to our top three.</p>'),
(670, 86, '_identity_design_story_2_identity_design_step', 'field_54f5ee84bbe80'),
(671, 86, 'identity_design_story_2_step_gallery_0_gallery_photo', '71'),
(672, 86, '_identity_design_story_2_step_gallery_0_gallery_photo', 'field_54f630beed2a5'),
(673, 86, 'identity_design_story_2_step_gallery', '1'),
(674, 86, '_identity_design_story_2_step_gallery', 'field_54f630a5ed2a4'),
(675, 86, 'identity_design_story_3_identity_design_step', '<h4 class="p1">Color, Pattern, &amp; Font Selection</h4>\r\n<p class="p1">Having developed a graphic that spoke to the unique qualities of the Shanghai Quartet, our next move was to hand pick the fonts, colors, and patterns that would best support the quartet’s new graphic identity. GriffosFont was selected for the wordmark based on its old-world, hand-chiseled look; the tail on the Q was elongated to add to the unique character of the mark.</p>'),
(676, 86, '_identity_design_story_3_identity_design_step', 'field_54f5ee84bbe80'),
(677, 86, 'identity_design_story_3_step_gallery_0_gallery_photo', '73'),
(678, 86, '_identity_design_story_3_step_gallery_0_gallery_photo', 'field_54f630beed2a5'),
(679, 86, 'identity_design_story_3_step_gallery', '1'),
(680, 86, '_identity_design_story_3_step_gallery', 'field_54f630a5ed2a4'),
(681, 86, 'identity_design_story_4_identity_design_step', '<p class="p1">A Baroque background pattern was chosen based on the association of that era with the dawn of chamber music, and for its luxurious connotations. The colors—dark blue, ivory, and gold—were likewise chosen for their association in Western cultures with royalty and refinement, driving home the point that listening to a performance by the Shanghai Quartet has the power to whisk one away from the gritty details and worries of everyday life.</p>'),
(682, 86, '_identity_design_story_4_identity_design_step', 'field_54f5ee84bbe80'),
(683, 86, 'identity_design_story_4_step_gallery_0_gallery_photo', '72'),
(684, 86, '_identity_design_story_4_step_gallery_0_gallery_photo', 'field_54f630beed2a5'),
(685, 86, 'identity_design_story_4_step_gallery', '1'),
(686, 86, '_identity_design_story_4_step_gallery', 'field_54f630a5ed2a4'),
(687, 86, 'identity_design_story', '5'),
(688, 86, '_identity_design_story', 'field_54f5ee6dbbe7f'),
(689, 86, 'website_design_story_0_website_design_step', '<h4 class="p1">Photography Selection &amp; Integration</h4>\r\n<p class="p1">The Shanghai Quartet had plenty of publicity photos on hand when we met them, but none of these seemed to communicate the powerful energy of their performances. We worked closely with their photographer to develop a portfolio of live performance photos, which were used throughout the website for maximum impact.</p>'),
(690, 86, '_website_design_story_0_website_design_step', 'field_54f5eef6bbe82'),
(691, 86, 'website_design_story_0_web_step_gallery_0_web_gallery_photo', '70'),
(692, 86, '_website_design_story_0_web_step_gallery_0_web_gallery_photo', 'field_54f63106ed2a7'),
(693, 86, 'website_design_story_0_web_step_gallery_1_web_gallery_photo', '71'),
(694, 86, '_website_design_story_0_web_step_gallery_1_web_gallery_photo', 'field_54f63106ed2a7'),
(695, 86, 'website_design_story_0_web_step_gallery_2_web_gallery_photo', '72'),
(696, 86, '_website_design_story_0_web_step_gallery_2_web_gallery_photo', 'field_54f63106ed2a7'),
(697, 86, 'website_design_story_0_web_step_gallery', '3'),
(698, 86, '_website_design_story_0_web_step_gallery', 'field_54f630eeed2a6'),
(699, 86, 'website_design_story_1_website_design_step', '<h4 class="p1">Custom Performance Calendar</h4>\r\n<p class="p1">With their busy schedules, we knew that none of the quartet’s members would have the time to manually enter information on upcoming performances—so we made sure that their public calendar could be easily updated through Google Calendar, without sacrificing aesthetics or ease of use for those getting their information through the quartet’s website.</p>'),
(700, 86, '_website_design_story_1_website_design_step', 'field_54f5eef6bbe82'),
(701, 86, 'website_design_story_1_web_step_gallery_0_web_gallery_photo', '81'),
